title: Did Dr. Zelenko successfully treat 669 Corona virus patients?
subtitle: A written article confirming that people responded well to CAVID-19's experimental therapy is by no means an evidence-based contribution to science.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: Dr. Vladimir Zelenko ' s patients 669 COVID-19 who were treated with a mixture of hydrochlorquine, Azythromycin, and zinc did not witness any hospitalization, complications, or deaths.
